1 for this purpose at an earlier date. No later than January 1, 2029, the Commission shall initiate a
2 process to review the reasonableness of the proposed costs of the associated renewable energy
3 credits, and the costs to be passed on to the ratepayers, prior to the execution of a contract between
4 the systems and a swine waste generator. Reasonableness of the costs being proposed should
5 include the costs of other renewable energy credits. The systems shall not pass along any costs
6 to the ratepayers deemed by the Commission to be unreasonable.
