4 SEVERABILITY/EFFECTIVE DATE
5 SECTION 12. If any section or provision of this act is declared unconstitutional or
6 invalid by the courts, it does not affect the validity of this act as a whole or any part other than
7 the part so declared to be unconstitutional or invalid.
8 SECTION 13. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
9 law.
